## Step 5 — Start the development server

    npm run dev

Open http://localhost:3000 in your browser.

You should see a home page with Sign in and Create account buttons.

### Pages that are ready

    /            Home page
    /login       Login page (add your form using shadcn Input and Button)
    /register    Register page (add your form using shadcn Input and Button)
    /dashboard   Protected — automatically redirects to /login if not signed in

